text: Werner Hartmann (born 20 February 1942) is an Austrian wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman flyweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Austria Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg Category:People from Feldkirch District
